body_html: I ran into the a similar issue in a new Python 3.6 virtual environment. The issue was resolved when I updated my machine with the Python 3.6 development package. This link has information to resolve this on various platforms: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/21530577/fatal-error-python-h-no-such-file-or-directory
